lead_paragraph: A student activist who had been hanging since Friday from the anchor chain of an oil-drilling support ship to protest Royal Dutch Shell’s plans to drill for oil ended her protest on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Washington: Protester Lets Go of Ship
headline.main: Washington: Protester Lets Go of Ship

snippet: A student activist who had been hanging since Friday from the anchor chain of an oil-drilling support ship to protest Royal Dutch Shell’s plans to drill for oil ended her protest on Monday.
abstract: Student activist Chiara D'Angelo ends three-day protest, in which she hung from anchor chain of an oil-drilling platform, over Royal Dutch Shell's plans to drill for oil.
